Aku mohon padamu.

298
00:21:10,840 --> 00:21:11,920
Bantulah aku.

299
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:14,640
Aku bantu memijat pundak dan kakimu.

300
00:21:17,520 --> 00:21:19,040
Aku mohon padamu.

301
00:21:20,120 --> 00:21:20,800
Kemarikan.

302
